{"tid":2075501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"UN出tweet支持Anifa既‘言論自由’及‘和平集會權利’ 俾人屌到del 番","createTime":"2020-06-23T01:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T10:25:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f31151c602f7b9bccd41f75bc13b20e1116266d6","tid":2075501,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T01:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgn8UQt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqgn8UQt.png&h=6d07a0ef&s={SIZE}\" />The United Nations Office at Geneva (UNOG) deleted a tweet they posted to Twitter on Friday after receiving public backlash for defending Antifa's right to &quot;freedom of expression&quot; and &quot;peaceful assembly.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe original tweet showed the Antifa flag with the text: &ldquo;UN Human Rights experts express profound concern over a recent statement by the US Attorney-General describing Antifa and other anti-fascist activists as domestic terrorists, saying it undermines the rights to freedom of expression and of peaceful assembly in the country.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thepostmillennial.com/un-deletes-tweet-supporting-antifa-after-public-backlash\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthepostmillennial.com%2Fun-deletes-tweet-supporting-antifa-after-public-backlash&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7vtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=5e49228d\" target=\"_blank\">https://thepostmillennial.com/un-deletes-tweet-supporting-antifa-after-public-backlash</a>"},{"pid":"858be85cb0a742ebb3858ad68b1d79e854f1ba09","tid":2075501,"uid":282347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T01:45:21.000Z","msg":"UN係咪舊年六月九號訓到依家，啱啱訓醒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26639291b04476f2120a80a938e6d345f99d8bde","tid":2075501,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020